					"value": "- Recruit companion Karlach\r\n- For normal default branch:\r\n     SetGlobalOsirisFlag GLO_Daisy_State_Unlocked\r\n- For astral tadpole branch:\r\n     SetGlobalOsirisFlag GLO_Tadpole_State_ReceivedAstralTadpole\r\n- Speak with her and select \"So - about our tadpole powers...\" or \"The Emperor has offered us a special tadpole. We'll become partial mind flayers, but we'll get great powers in turn...\""
